Class Description

Extension of JFrame.
GameRunner

Represents an image asset for this Fish Simulator.
ImageHolder
Holds assets for this Fish Simulator, which can be drawn to the screen
ImageLoader
Loads assets from a line of a CSV, which currently contains an asset path and immutability value.
Launcher
Launches the main Fish Simulator game
